{"tid":1781794,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【本月小喜訊】警察電單車西隧口相撞　兩警受傷送院","createTime":"2019-12-13T12:21:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-13T14:16:41.000Z","uid":165208,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"cff575f615be4141e2f973451d568a266eb7c5a1","tid":1781794,"uid":165208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T12:21:22.000Z","msg":"兩名警員駕駛電單車執勤時相撞同告受傷。今（8日）上午11時42分，兩輛警察電單車沿西區海底隧道往九龍方向行駛，當駛至近九龍出口收費廣場時，前車因應前方交通情況慢駛，後車同袍懷疑收掣不及撞向前車，一名男警腳傷，另一名男警腰痛及腳傷，兩名男警被送往伊利沙伯醫院治理，案件例作交通意外有人受傷。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E9%9B%BB%E5%96%AE%E8%BB%8A%E8%A5%BF%E9%9A%A7%E5%8F%A3%E7%9B%B8%E6%92%9E-%E5%85%A9%E8%AD%A6%E5%8F%97%E5%82%B7%E9%80%81%E9%99%A2-094217102.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25AF%259F%25E9%259B%25BB%25E5%2596%25AE%25E8%25BB%258A%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E9%259A%25A7%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%259B%25B8%25E6%2592%259E-%25E5%2585%25A9%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%258F%2597%25E5%2582%25B7%25E9%2580%2581%25E9%2599%25A2-094217102.html&d=ZRuO0gn2PDb4CPS%2BM%2Fpj6maNvfBTe1ydx6p2nKz01sw%3D&h=ce57f3c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E9%9B%BB%E5%96%AE%E8%BB%8A%E8%A5%BF%E9%9A%A7%E5%8F%A3%E7%9B%B8%E6%92%9E-%E5%85%A9%E8%AD%A6%E5%8F%97%E5%82%B7%E9%80%81%E9%99%A2-094217102.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n死垃圾炒車破壞公物 又要市民埋單"},{"pid":"86f948415cbd1106a46e143ccf15cb5d7f12f570","tid":1781794,"uid":307749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T12:21:58.000Z","msg":"好弱"},{"pid":"90aa72789cc36ab134f6219730a1a1d91bc34b49","tid":1781794,"uid":238138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T12:23:27.000Z","msg":"好開心"},{"pid":"b37e8834d168defb2919b0327d1e2838dc094be3","tid":1781794,"uid":213978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T12:24:35.000Z","msg":"香檳"},{"pid":"76a8c399a869d83c76c16661f5f5ca2c64cbcd35","tid":1781794,"uid